name: Ego
description:
In Latin the word 'ego' means 'I' .
Ego is something we all battle if
you look deep within and over
time try to adjust. It's a constant
struggle to keep your ego in good
health. Self-importance,
self-esteem, worth, respect,
confidence and self-image. Ego
can be overpowering for some
both positively and negatively.
